{"tid":1380261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"消防員有野想同「新界西的女孩」講","createTime":"2019-07-29T03:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T03:59:42.000Z","uid":39355,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5b7f10f43bb8c4faca0367bd78683d55b53628cd","tid":1380261,"uid":39355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:30:43.000Z","msg":"事源有位中學同學係消防員，佢喺Facebook 睇到一封寄去元朗消防局既信（下圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dSc1XCu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdSc1XCu.png&h=1656abe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbQbApT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbQbApT.png&h=2c2cb80c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢好擔心寫信果位女生，但佢又唔知點聯絡佢，所以託我幫手貼上連登，以下係我位消防朋友既回覆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fa2Yfqi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFa2Yfqi.png&h=4d595051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信除左我呢位消防員朋友睇到外，<br />\n亦都有其他消防員會睇到，而且大家都希望各位可以保持希望。<br />\n<br />\n如果有人識寄信果位女生，希望大家睇住佢，<br />\n同佢講消防員都希望佢可以繼續努力，<br />\n我地唔想再有人輕生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油！<br />\n<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a559208dbd8702f667ac5ed7c6091ec9d601865","tid":1380261,"uid":234270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:33:44.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2902879a8a8d9d9e0d9ae9abcd823cf0c928bf","tid":1380261,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb72e640c31c91487d613ab0451d69d81d6f405d","tid":1380261,"uid":276510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:35:58.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":